<% message.subject = "#{@inviting_user.name} would like you to contribute to their Médecins Sans Frontières research study (#{@study.reference_number})" %>
Hi <%= @invited_user.name %>,

<%= @inviting_user.name %> (<%= @inviting_user.email %>) has invited you to contribute to their study:

<%= @study.title %>

on the Médecins Sans Frontières ReMIT website.

You can click this link:

<%= "#{study_outputs_new_url(@study)}?token=#{@invited_user.invite_token}" %>

at any time and there you'll find forms to describe any disseminations or other impact this study has had.

Many thanks,

MSF ReMIT team.